
<div class="box box-default">


<div class="box-header with-border">
 <h3 class="box-title"> Certificate Of Promotion </h3>
     <div class="pull-right">
   <%= link_to "Print Certificate",print_certificate_employee_promotions_path(id: @employee_promotion.id,format: "pdf") ,class: 'btn btn-primary btn-sm ',:target => "_blank"%> 
  </div>

</div>
<!-- <div class="pull-right">

   </div> -->
  <div class="box-body">
<div style="width: 500px; height: 690px;
            font-size: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 2px solid gray;
            margin-right: 150px;
            margin-left: 300px;">

  <td colspan="4"><b><b><center>Certificate Of Promotion</center></b></b></td><hr>
  <tr><td colspan="4"><center><strong><%= @employee_promotion.employee.company_location.company.try(:description) %></strong> <br>
        <%= @employee_promotion.employee.company_location.company.try(:address) %><br> 
        <%= @employee_promotion.employee.company_location.try(:name) %></center> </td></tr>
        <hr>
 
 <p> Dear Mr./Miss.<b> <%= @employee_promotion.employee.try(:first_name) %> <%= @employee_promotion.employee.try(:middle_name) %> <%= @employee_promotion.employee.try(:last_name) %> </b> </p>

 <p>This is in continuation to your application for the internal job posting for the department of <b><%= @employee_promotion.department.try(:name) %> </b>and your subsequent interview with our Board of Directors.</p>

 <p>We are extremely pleased to inform you that the Board has considered you suitable for the post. You have therefore been promoted to <b><%= @employee_promotion.employee_designation.try(:name) %></b> with effect from <b><%= @employee_promotion.effective_from %></b> </p>

 <p>By becoming the <b><%= @employee_promotion.employee_designation.try(:name) %></b> your CTC will now be Rs. <b><%= @employee_promotion.employee_ctc %></b> (per annum). Please contact the HR department for a break up of the CTC.</p>

 <p>Congratulations on your achievement and we wish you all the very best in the coming years.</p><br>

 <div style="float:left;">Best regards,<br>

 _____________<br>

(Name of signing authority)</div>


</div>

<br><br>
 <%= link_to 'Back',promotion_history_employee_promotions_path(id: @employee_promotion.employee_id),class: 'btn btn-default btn-sm fa fa-arrow-left'%>
